data.eml:eml: Description of a striking new Mantophryne species (Amphibia, Anura, Microhylidae) from Woodlark Island, Papua New Guinea

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Guenther, Rainer, Richards, Stephen (2016): Description of a striking new Mantophryne species (Amphibia, Anura, Microhylidae) from Woodlark Island, Papua New Guinea. Zoosystematics and Evolution 92 (1): 111-118, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.92.7629, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.92.7629
